  "description": [
    "Letters Continued from Page Two sweat and tears for a pittance Of course that would be too much like communism but all our young men are under a military dictatorship right now so why shouldnt we all get a taste of it Wouldnt that be the best way to scare people away from com munism And wouldnt it also show them that in time of war we really are placed under a military dictator ship except that a certain class of peo ple are allowed to pile up money during war and so are exempt to a certain from this dictatorship Ship and others are offered fat contracts to induce them to serve degree builders war their government How are they any better than the boys who are con scripted and forced to be patriotic Woudnt a demand for total con majority of the peo scription by a pie really be an eyeopener and jerk out of that complacency that needs to fear according everyone democracy to N 1 Dougherty the recent attempt to kill Just as the coops by taxation woke everyone up to the danger and sent them into action We need something now to wake people up"
  ],
